	* gnumeric-expr-entry.c : Move from
	  ABS_COL/ABS_ROW -> FORCE_ABS/FORCE_REL
	  All callers changed.

2007-10-21  Morten Welinder <terra@gnome.org>

	* Release 1.7.13

