2006-12-17  Jody Goldberg <jody@gnome.org>

	* Release 1.7.6

2006-12-08  Jody Goldberg <jody@gnome.org>

	* gnm-filter-combo-foo-view.c (formatted_value_equal) : differentiate
	  between the same value with different formats (100% vs $1)

