2001-05-20  Jody Goldberg <jgoldberg@home.com>

	* Release 0.65

2001-05-15  Almer S. Tigelaar  <almer@gnome.org>

	* gnumeric-hscrollbar.c (gnumeric_hscrollbar_button_press): Adjust
